= IMG_LoadAnimation_RW =

Load an animation from an SDL datasource 

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
IMG_Animation * IMG_LoadAnimation_RW(SDL_RWops *src, int freesrc);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''src'''
|RWops
|-
|'''freesrc'''
|can be set so that the RWops is freed after this function is called
|}

== Return Value ==

Returns IMG Animation, or NULL on error

== Version ==

This function is available since SDL_image 2.6.0.

